{
  "stem": "33.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But a lot of Jewish men were severely beaten, because they did not believe them that they gave all their money, all their jewelry, everything away.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had to give everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Before we got into the ghetto we couldn't even keep a watch, anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I think the only thing they let you keep, if I remember correctly, was maybe a wedding ring.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They would let you keep that, but I'm not sure of that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But everything else, you couldn't keep money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You couldn't keep jewelry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You couldn't-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I mean, absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You had to give everything away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And there were some severe beatings by the Hungarian police, the Hungarian gendarme, which is a section of the police, a branch of the Hungarian police.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The ghetto-- as I said, the ghetto itself wasn't that horrible, because we were told that we are going to be resettled in Germany and we are going to work in factories or on the fields, wherever our labor is needed for the Nazi war economy.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we were assured that work will be hard, but we will be OK.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We'll be treated well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Resettlement was the word that were used.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They started taking people away, 3,000 at the time, as soon as we were all in the ghetto area, which was about the middle of May.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Now, [SIGHS] you know, 6 million people, 11 million people all together, were murdered in this period of time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It is a very large number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You cannot mourn that many people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "In my case, of course, since I had no siblings, it was basically my parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I had one grandparent, a grandmother who was 81 years old, who was a great-grandmother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She had two seven-year-old great-grandsons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Actually, at 18, I was her youngest grandchild.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
